## Amigaguide documentation for Reset 3.1

@NODE MAIN "Reset.doc"

                                 Reset

                       Version 3.1 on 3/30/1994
                          by Martin Schlodder

    This is version 3.1 of Reset, an update to the version 3.03.

This program only runs with  OS 2.0 or higher.  It behaves like a typical CLI
command through the use of ReadArgs(). If run with OS 2.1 or higher, it is
fully localized.

